  ('elementary-6f0ba476-moex-00949', 'elementary-6f0ba476', 'elementary-6f0ba476-moex-110-4bd2866a', 'sub-elementary-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關稅式支出之敘述，何者正確？', '["政府對於政策鼓勵事項給予租稅優惠措施，此類應收未收之稅負，可視為廣義之公共支出", "政府從事某項公共建設後，對受益民眾另行課徵租稅，以支應該支出款項", "政府徵收租稅後，因期末支出有剩餘，將此剩餘發還給納稅人", "政府徵收租稅後，被限定支出用途，此即指定用途稅之支出"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "823acbf432c6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "254e7c083307", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "507", "s": "0503", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "財政學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-6f0ba476-moex-00950', 'elementary-6f0ba476', 'elementary-6f0ba476-moex-110-4bd2866a', 'sub-elementary-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那種投票者的特性，可能造成多數決的矛盾現象？', '["排他性", "非排他性", "雙峰偏好", "非敵對性"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "823acbf432c6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "254e7c083307", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "507", "s": "0503", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "財政學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-6f0ba476-moex-00951', 'elementary-6f0ba476', 'elementary-6f0ba476-moex-110-4bd2866a', 'sub-elementary-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '每個投票者皆有固定點數，可以根據其偏好將點數分配予不同選項。此為何種投票法則？', '["一致決", "辛辛那提投票法則（Cincinnatirule）", "康多塞投票制（Condorcetelections）", "點投票（pointvoting）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "823acbf432c6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "254e7c083307", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "507", "s": "0503", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "財政學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
